page.title: 14A SCHOOL DAY(FRIDAY).
page.content: At 8am I jumped out of bed dashed downstairs.I quickly ate my breakfast, grabbed my school bag and ran for the bus. 8.50am Morning Registration+Assembly 9.15am First Lesson(Double English). 10.25am Morning Break(15mins). 10.40am Double Home Economics. 11.50am Dinner(1 Hour) 12.50pm Afernoon Registration. 1.00pm Double Biology. 2.10pm Religous Education. 2.45pm English. 3.20pm HOME TIME! I arrive home about 4.00pm.I get changed,do my homework,put my books away and go to meet my friends in the park.I come in at 10.00pm.
